data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath residence boasts a modern open floor plan with a touch of elegance. Step inside to discover luxury vinyl plank flooring, creating a seamless and stylish ambiance. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, a large island for culinary adventures, all-white backsplash, and a convenient pantry for storage. Upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits with its en-suite bathroom, providing a private retreat. Two additional generously sized bedrooms and a conveniently located laundry area complete the upper level. The finished lower level is an entertainment haven, showcasing a vast rec room, an extra bedroom, and a full bath. Step outside to a sprawling backyard, complete with a spacious composite deck – an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. This home is not only a haven of comfort but also strategically located with close access to highways, shopping centers, schools, and scenic walking trails. Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously designed and conveniently situated home yours!
